1
00:00:24,959 --> 00:00:27,659
<i>[ Indistinct Whisper ]</i>

2
00:00:27,727 --> 00:00:32,030
JAROD? JAROD. DANGER.

3
00:00:32,099 --> 00:00:35,099
HATE! HATE DESTROY JAROD!

4
00:00:36,936 --> 00:00:41,439
[ Gasps, Panting ]

5
00:00:44,244 --> 00:00:49,447
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN!

6
00:00:51,184 --> 00:00:54,853
OPEN UP YOUR HEART!

7
00:00:54,921 --> 00:00:57,855
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN!

8
00:00:57,924 --> 00:01:01,360
LET THE HEALING START!

9
00:01:01,428 --> 00:01:05,530
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN!

10
00:01:07,767 --> 00:01:10,568
OPEN UP YOUR HEART.

11
00:01:11,571 --> 00:01:15,273
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN.
LET THE--

12
00:01:15,342 --> 00:01:17,776
<i>[ Children Singing ]</i>
<i>♪ HEALING START ♪</i>

13
00:01:17,845 --> 00:01:21,046
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪</i>

14
00:01:21,115 --> 00:01:25,183
<i>♪ OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪</i>

15
00:01:25,252 --> 00:01:27,886
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪♪

16
00:01:27,955 --> 00:01:31,389
VERY GOOD. VERY GOOD.
YOU SOUND LIKE TWO ANGELS.

17
00:01:31,458 --> 00:01:33,792
AND I CAN'T WAIT
TO HEAR YOU AT THE RALLY.

18
00:01:33,860 --> 00:01:36,394
- THANKS, DADDY.
- ALL RIGHT. I GOTTA
GET YOU TWO HOME, OKAY?

19
00:01:36,463 --> 00:01:39,064
YOU GOT A BIG WEEKEND
AHEAD OF YOU.
FINISH YOUR HOMEWORK?

20
00:01:39,133 --> 00:01:42,634
I DID, BUT KATI DIDN'T.
'CAUSE I WAS
TOO BUSY DOIN' YOURS.

21
00:01:42,702 --> 00:01:46,404
OKAY, THAT'S ENOUGH OF THAT.
WE HAVE PLENTY OF TIME
BEFORE WE GO TO BED.

22
00:01:46,473 --> 00:01:48,406
OKAY, LET'S HEAR YOU
PRACTICE THAT SONG AGAIN.

23
00:01:48,475 --> 00:01:50,408
DADDY!
UH-UH.
PRACTICE MAKES WHAT?

24
00:01:50,477 --> 00:01:52,110
[ Girls ]
PERFECT.
ALL RIGHT, HERE WE GO.

25
00:01:52,179 --> 00:01:55,080
[ Together ]
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪

26
00:01:55,148 --> 00:01:58,450
♪ OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪
VERY GOOD.

27
00:01:58,519 --> 00:02:02,420
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN
OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪♪

28
00:02:02,489 --> 00:02:06,591
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>EVENIN', PASTOR JONES!</i>
DADDY!

29
00:02:08,595 --> 00:02:11,196
LISTEN, GENTLEMEN,
I'D APPRECIATE IT...

30
00:02:11,265 --> 00:02:14,466
IF YOU ALL JUST TURN
RIGHT AROUND AND GO BACK
WHERE YOU CAME FROM.

31
00:02:14,535 --> 00:02:19,104
THAT'S NOT VERY FRIENDLY COMIN'
FROM A CIVIL RIGHTS LEADER
FAMOUS FOR PREACHIN' UNITY!

32
00:02:19,172 --> 00:02:21,106
- [ Man Yells ]
- [ Girls Screaming ]

33
00:02:21,174 --> 00:02:24,009
- NO, NO. IT'S OKAY.
- OF COURSE, SOME OF US HAVE
A DIFFERENT OPINION...

34
00:02:24,077 --> 00:02:26,945
ABOUT THE WORLD BEIN'
UNDER ONE BIG RAINBOW AND SUCH.

35
00:02:27,014 --> 00:02:29,514
- [ Men ] YEAH!
- [ Girl ] WHO ARE THEY?

36
00:02:29,583 --> 00:02:33,218
- BACK INSIDE NOW!
- I SAY WE SHOW PASTOR JONES
THE LIGHT...

37
00:02:33,286 --> 00:02:35,853
<i> THE WAY WE SEE IT!</i>

38
00:02:35,922 --> 00:02:38,624
<i>[ Men Shouting, Whooping ]</i>

39
00:02:38,692 --> 00:02:42,026
- GO ON!
- LET'S GO. GET DOWN.

40
00:02:42,095 --> 00:02:44,563
GET DOWN. GET DOWN!
[ Girls Screaming ]

41
00:02:44,631 --> 00:02:46,831
GET DOWN!
<i>[ Glass Shattering ]</i>

42
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:49,034
<i>[ Whooping Continues ]</i>

43
00:02:51,839 --> 00:02:55,674
<i>[ Men Shouting ]</i>
MAKE 'EM STOP!

44
00:02:57,277 --> 00:02:59,577
[ Screaming ]
IT'S OKAY.

45
00:03:07,754 --> 00:03:09,887
GRAB THAT END!

46
00:03:10,924 --> 00:03:13,191
SET IT RIGHT HERE.

47
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:16,895
[ Whooping Continues ]

48
00:03:16,964 --> 00:03:19,998
GET OUT!
[ Shouting ]

49
00:03:25,805 --> 00:03:29,007
MAKE 'EM STOP!
IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.
DADDY'S HERE, BABY.

50
00:03:29,076 --> 00:03:32,343
[ Yelling, Laughing ]

51
00:03:32,412 --> 00:03:35,880
THIS IS YOUR LAST WARNING!
NOBODY WANTS UNITY
WITH YOU PEOPLE!

52
00:03:35,949 --> 00:03:39,217
<i>GET THE HELL OUTTA HERE</i>
<i>WHILE YOU STILL CAN!</i>

53
00:03:39,286 --> 00:03:42,053
[ Sobbing ]
WHY DO THEY DO THIS
TO US, DADDY? WHY?

54
00:03:42,122 --> 00:03:45,289
- OKAY, BABY. OKAY.
- I THINK WE MADE OUR POINT.

55
00:03:45,358 --> 00:03:48,427
[ Laughs ]

56
00:03:49,797 --> 00:03:52,397
YEAH, I THINK THEY GET
THE MESSAGE THIS TIME.

57
00:04:02,642 --> 00:04:05,210
<i>[ Vehicles Departing ]</i>

58
00:04:05,279 --> 00:04:07,478
[ Men Whooping ]

59
00:04:20,126 --> 00:04:23,261
<i>[ Man Narrating ]</i>
<i>THERE ARE PRETENDERS AMONG US.</i>

60
00:04:23,329 --> 00:04:25,263
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I WAS TAKEN FROM MY FAMILY.</i>

61
00:04:25,332 --> 00:04:28,900
<i>THIRTY-SIX HOURS AND HE'S</i>
<i>ALREADY DEMONSTRATING MORE</i>
<i>TALENT THAN ANY OF OUR OTHERS.</i>

62
00:04:28,969 --> 00:04:32,270
<i>HOW MANY PEOPLE DIED</i>
<i>BECAUSE OF WHAT I THOUGHT UP?</i>

63
00:04:32,339 --> 00:04:35,774
SINCE I BROKE OUT,
I'VE SPENT EVERY MOMENT
SEARCHING FOR MY PAST.

64
00:04:35,843 --> 00:04:38,043
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>HE'S A PRETENDER--</i>

65
00:04:38,112 --> 00:04:40,879
<i>A GENIUS WHO CAN BECOME</i>
<i>ANYONE THAT HE WANTS TO BE.</i>

66
00:04:40,948 --> 00:04:43,681
-<i> THE CENTRE WANTS HIM ALIVE.</i>
- PREFERABLY.

67
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:46,684
<i>- [ Miss Parker ] HE DEFENDS</i>
<i>  THE WEAK AND ABUSED.</i>
<i>- [ Jarod ] LIFE'S A GIFT.</i>

68
00:04:58,464 --> 00:05:00,932
-<i> YOU A DOCTOR?</i>
- I AM TODAY.

69
00:05:06,406 --> 00:05:08,339
[ Broots ]
ANGELO'S GONE POSTAL.

70
00:05:08,408 --> 00:05:11,909
HE'S GOING THROUGH THE EVIDENCE
FROM JAROD'S OLD PRETENDS,
AND HE'S FLIPPIN' OUT.

71
00:05:11,978 --> 00:05:14,679
THE LITTLE FREAK'S
POSSESSED.
HAS HE SAID ANYTHING?

72
00:05:14,748 --> 00:05:16,848
PLENTY. BUT NONE OF IT
MAKES ANY SENSE.

73
00:05:16,916 --> 00:05:21,419
FIRE! FIRE!

74
00:05:24,024 --> 00:05:27,059
<i> LIKE I SAID,</i>
<i> HE'S POSSESSED.</i>

75
00:05:35,134 --> 00:05:39,171
[ Groaning ]

76
00:05:39,239 --> 00:05:43,441
FIRE BURN! JAROD!
MUST HELP JAROD!

77
00:05:45,845 --> 00:05:48,679
- [ Groans ]
- ANGELO.

78
00:05:48,748 --> 00:05:51,249
<i>JAROD.</i>

79
00:05:51,318 --> 00:05:53,618
JAROD.

80
00:05:53,687 --> 00:05:55,353
[ Panting, Gasping ]

81
00:05:55,422 --> 00:05:57,455
WHAT'S WRONG?
WE MUST SAVE JAROD.

82
00:05:57,524 --> 00:05:58,790
FROM WHAT?

83
00:05:58,859 --> 00:06:02,260
FROM FIRE. FROM HATE.

84
00:06:02,329 --> 00:06:04,862
HATE KILLS.

85
00:06:04,931 --> 00:06:07,598
HATE WILL KILL JAROD.

86
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:13,571
<i>MUST SAVE JAROD.</i>

87
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,673
WHAT DO YOU MAKE OF IT, SYD?

88
00:06:15,742 --> 00:06:20,378
I BELIEVE ANGELO THINKS THAT
SOMEONE FROM JAROD'S PAST...

89
00:06:20,446 --> 00:06:22,880
IS GOING TO TRY AND KILL HIM.

90
00:06:22,949 --> 00:06:26,351
<i>[ Angelo ]</i>
<i>JAROD. WE MUST SAVE JAROD!</i>

91
00:06:28,388 --> 00:06:31,322
THE QUESTION IS, WHO?
<i> [ Angelo Yells ]</i>

92
00:06:34,862 --> 00:06:37,362
[ Angelo Yells ]

93
00:06:43,003 --> 00:06:47,105
[ Men Whooping ]

94
00:06:55,582 --> 00:06:58,750
[ Indistinct Shouting ]

95
00:06:58,818 --> 00:07:02,454
I'D SAY WE LEARNED PASTOR JONES
A LESSON OR TWO TONIGHT!
WHOO!

96
00:07:02,523 --> 00:07:06,090
WELL, A LITTLE VISUAL AID
ALWAYS HELPED MY THIRD-GRADE
STUDENTS GET THE POINT.

97
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,993
I'D SAY A BURNING CROSS
IS A LOT MORE EFFECTIVE
THAN A FILMSTRIP.

98
00:07:09,062 --> 00:07:11,162
I GUESS WE SHOWED HIM
THE LIGHT, HUH, JAROD?

99
00:07:11,231 --> 00:07:13,030
IF A PICTURE'S
WORTH A THOUSAND WORDS,

100
00:07:13,099 --> 00:07:16,234
<i> A FLAMIN' CROSS</i>
<i> IS WORTH A MOUTHFUL!</i>

101
00:07:16,303 --> 00:07:18,669
- YEAH!
- [ Whooping ]

102
00:07:18,738 --> 00:07:21,506
IT OUGHTA BE
AGAINST THE LAW
TO HAVE THAT MUCH FUN.

103
00:07:21,574 --> 00:07:24,042
IN FACT, I BELIEVE
IT<i> IS</i> AGAINST THE LAW.

104
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:28,012
- [ All Laughing ]
- IT BEATS THE HELL OUTTA
SELLIN' LIFE INSURANCE.

105
00:07:28,081 --> 00:07:30,381
- I SAY WE GO CELEBRATE!
- [ All Cheering ]

106
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:33,051
<i>NO, NOBODY'S GOIN' ANYWHERE.</i>
<i>CHANGE OF PLANS.</i>

107
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:37,222
<i>-IS THERE SOMETHIN' WRONG?</i>
-WHILE YOU WERE ALL OUT PLAYIN',
I GOT A CALL FROM THE GENERAL.

108
00:07:37,291 --> 00:07:39,357
THE GENERAL?

109
00:07:40,627 --> 00:07:42,960
WHAT'D HE WANT?

110
00:07:43,029 --> 00:07:45,596
HE'S COMIN' IN EARLY.
HE COULD BE HERE ANYTIME.

111
00:07:45,665 --> 00:07:48,433
SO, WHY'S THAT CHANGE
OUR PLAN?

112
00:07:48,502 --> 00:07:51,603
'CAUSE HE'S GOT A NEW
MISSION. A BOLD MESSAGE.

113
00:07:51,672 --> 00:07:53,938
ONE THAT'S JUST NOT GONNA
BE HEARD AROUND THE COUNTRY.

114
00:07:54,007 --> 00:07:56,474
IT'S GONNA BE HEARD
AROUND THE WORLD.

115
00:07:56,543 --> 00:07:58,810
- THAT SOUNDS BIG.
- YEAH, IT IS, DONNY.

116
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:01,613
AND ON ACCOUNT OF THAT,
HE WANTS EACH OF YOU HERE
WHEN HE SHOWS UP.

117
00:08:01,681 --> 00:08:04,816
- WE GOTTA STAY HERE ALL NIGHT?
- WAIT. WE CAN'T GO ANYWHERE?

118
00:08:04,885 --> 00:08:06,784
UNTIL HE SHOWS UP.

119
00:08:08,054 --> 00:08:10,621
Y'ALL BEEN RECRUITED
FROM OUTSIDE THE STATE.

120
00:08:10,690 --> 00:08:13,291
<i> THE GENERAL'S WORRIED</i>
<i> YOU GO INTO TOWN,</i>

121
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:16,161
AND YOU'LL STAND OUT
LIKE A RACCOON IN A HENHOUSE.

122
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:18,830
NOW, I GOT A LITTLE GIFT
HERE FROM THE GENERAL...

123
00:08:18,898 --> 00:08:21,432
HE WANTS US TO USE
TO DELIVER OUR MESSAGE.

124
00:08:25,739 --> 00:08:28,172
- C-4 EXPLOSIVE?
- YEAH.

125
00:08:30,744 --> 00:08:33,778
WELL, THAT PACKS
A HELL OF A PUNCH.

126
00:08:33,847 --> 00:08:36,113
<i>DAMN RIGHT.</i>
<i>YOU'RE OUR DEMOLITION EXPERT.</i>

127
00:08:36,182 --> 00:08:40,618
YOU'RE GONNA RIG US UP
A LITTLE DEVICE TO DIS-UNIFY
THIS UNITY RALLY!

128
00:08:40,687 --> 00:08:43,455
- [ Laughing ]
- I'LL TELL YOU SOMETHIN', BOYS.

129
00:08:43,523 --> 00:08:47,258
WHEN WE'RE FINISHED,
THE PARTYIN' AIN'T GONNA STOP.

130
00:08:47,326 --> 00:08:51,429
- [ All Cheering ]
- YEAH!

131
00:08:51,498 --> 00:08:53,698
YEAH! WHOO!

132
00:08:53,766 --> 00:08:56,201
<i> [ Dispatcher ]</i>
<i> A FLAG DOWN</i>
<i> AT 4581 PROSPECT STREET.</i>

133
00:08:56,269 --> 00:08:58,903
HOW LONG HAS THIS
CRAZINESS BEEN GOIN' ON?

134
00:08:58,972 --> 00:09:01,839
SEVERAL WEEKS AGO,
WE ORGANIZED A UNITY RALLY.

135
00:09:01,908 --> 00:09:04,142
THIS EVENT'S SUPPOSED
TO BRING TOGETHER...

136
00:09:04,211 --> 00:09:07,145
PEOPLE FROM THE COMMUNITY
FROM ALL WALKS OF LIFE.

137
00:09:07,214 --> 00:09:11,449
WELL, AFTER SUPPORT GREW,
THAT'S WHEN WE STARTED
RECEIVIN' THREATS.

138
00:09:11,518 --> 00:09:14,386
WHAT KIND OF THREATS?
WARNINGS.

139
00:09:14,454 --> 00:09:17,288
TELLIN' US
TO CALL OFF THE RALLY.
AND WHEN YOU DIDN'T?

140
00:09:17,357 --> 00:09:20,825
THAT'S WHEN THE ACTS
OF VANDALISM BEGAN...

141
00:09:20,894 --> 00:09:22,827
LEADIN' UP TO LAST NIGHT.

142
00:09:22,896 --> 00:09:25,230
LOOK, PASTOR,
THE RALLY'S TOMORROW.

143
00:09:25,298 --> 00:09:27,665
THESE TYPES PROBABLY
AREN'T GOING AWAY. MAYBE--

144
00:09:27,734 --> 00:09:30,201
MAYBE WHAT, SHERIFF? HUH?

145
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:34,538
MAYBE WE SHOULD JUST
GIVE IN, HUH? GIVE IN AND
JUST CALL THE WHOLE THING OFF.

146
00:09:34,607 --> 00:09:37,008
NO, SHERIFF.
THAT'S EXACTLY WHAT THEY WANT.

147
00:09:37,076 --> 00:09:39,811
POSTPONE IT.
THINK ABOUT YOUR GIRLS.

148
00:09:43,783 --> 00:09:46,251
YOU KNOW, SHERIFF,
WHEN I WAS 13,

149
00:09:46,319 --> 00:09:49,788
I SAW A MAN BEATEN
AND DRAGGED BEHIND A TRUCK,

150
00:09:49,856 --> 00:09:53,057
AND NOBODY
DID NOTHIN' TO STOP IT.

151
00:09:54,627 --> 00:09:56,561
NOT EVEN ME.

152
00:09:57,931 --> 00:10:00,698
THAT MAN LIVED
FOR THREE DAYS,

153
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:04,168
THE WHOLE TIME
PRAYIN' TO DIE.

154
00:10:07,573 --> 00:10:10,241
THAT MAN, SHERIFF,
WAS MY BIG BROTHER.

155
00:10:12,011 --> 00:10:14,045
SEE, IF YOU DON'T FIX
THIS KIND OF HATE,

156
00:10:14,114 --> 00:10:16,848
IT WILL DESTROY
EVERYONE THAT IT TOUCHES.

157
00:10:18,385 --> 00:10:21,319
IT'S BECAUSE OF MY DAUGHTERS
I GOTTA DO THIS.

158
00:10:21,388 --> 00:10:23,754
SO YES, SIR.

159
00:10:23,823 --> 00:10:27,191
YES, I WILL BE AT THAT RALLY
TOMORROW WITH MY CHURCH...

160
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:29,193
AND MY FAMILY.

161
00:10:51,985 --> 00:10:54,018
ANY PROGRESS?

162
00:10:54,087 --> 00:10:58,289
ANGELO SENSES THAT SOMEONE
JAROD BROUGHT TO JUSTICE...

163
00:10:58,358 --> 00:11:00,558
IS GOING TO TRY TO KILL HIM.

164
00:11:00,627 --> 00:11:03,494
WE'RE TRYING TO FIND OUT WHO
BY LETTING HIM EMPATH...

165
00:11:03,562 --> 00:11:06,897
<i>VARIOUS ITEMS THE CENTRE</i>
<i>RECOVERED FROM PAST PRETENDS.</i>

166
00:11:06,966 --> 00:11:11,001
I'M CERTAINLY NOT SURPRISED
SOMEONE FROM JAROD'S PAST
WANTS TO KILL HIM.

167
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:14,272
IN FACT, THAT'S
A HELL OF A LONG LINE,
AND IT STARTS BEHIND ME.

168
00:11:18,979 --> 00:11:21,278
HEY, LOOK. THAT'S THE DRESS
THE BLACK WIDOW WAS WEARING.

169
00:11:21,347 --> 00:11:24,482
<i>THE ONE THAT JAROD TOOK DOWN</i>
<i>FOR MURDERING HER HUSBAND.</i>

170
00:11:25,885 --> 00:11:28,086
<i> SHE CERTAINLY</i>
<i> HAS ENOUGH REASON.</i>

171
00:11:28,154 --> 00:11:30,554
AND SHE DID TRY
TO KILL HIM ONCE.

172
00:11:34,361 --> 00:11:36,794
[ Whispering ]
DOES HE THINK IT'S HER?

173
00:11:39,266 --> 00:11:42,467
I WANT THIS TO BE OVER.

174
00:11:42,536 --> 00:11:44,802
I KNOW YOU DO.

175
00:11:47,874 --> 00:11:52,476
JAROD? I LOVE YOU.

176
00:12:12,966 --> 00:12:15,700
[ Yells, Mutters ]

177
00:12:15,769 --> 00:12:20,171
<i> JAROD'S IN DANGER!</i>
<i> BUT NOT HER. NOT A WOMAN.</i>

178
00:12:23,142 --> 00:12:25,910
<i> SYD, DOES HE EVEN KNOW</i>
<i> WHAT HE'S DOING?</i>

179
00:12:25,978 --> 00:12:27,912
JAROD DOESN'T KNOW.

180
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:32,583
ANGELO IS SYSTEMATICALLY
EVALUATING AND ELIMINATING
INDIVIDUALS IN JAROD'S PAST...

181
00:12:32,652 --> 00:12:35,019
WITH THE MOST INTENSE
FEELINGS OF HATRED FOR HIM.

182
00:12:35,087 --> 00:12:37,722
THEN WE NEED TO KEEP THIS
FROM LYLE AND RAINES.

183
00:12:37,791 --> 00:12:39,924
THEY'LL ONLY INTERFERE
WITH ANGELO'S PROGRESS.

184
00:12:39,993 --> 00:12:44,228
THEN WE'D BETTER MOVE FAST,
BECAUSE, UH, SECRETS
AREN'T KEPT LONG AROUND HERE.

185
00:12:44,297 --> 00:12:48,399
IF ANGELO CAN SUCCESSFULLY
ISOLATE THE POTENTIAL KILLER,
HE CAN TAKE US TO HIM.

186
00:12:48,468 --> 00:12:51,535
- AND TO JAROD?
- HOPEFULLY IN TIME TO SAVE HIM.

187
00:12:51,604 --> 00:12:54,339
EVEN BETTER,
IN TIME TO CATCH HIM.

188
00:13:05,251 --> 00:13:08,920
[ Dog Barking ]

189
00:13:26,672 --> 00:13:30,308
<i>♪♪ [ Hip-hop Beat ]</i>

190
00:13:33,813 --> 00:13:36,614
<i>[ Laughing ]</i>

191
00:13:36,683 --> 00:13:39,917
<i>HEY, TURN THAT DAMN THING OFF,</i>
<i>WILL YA? JUNGLE MUSIC.</i>

192
00:13:41,854 --> 00:13:45,422
CAN'T EVEN LISTEN
TO THE RADIO ANYMORE
WITHOUT HEARIN' THAT CRAP.

193
00:13:46,859 --> 00:13:49,260
AIN'T YOU ABOUT DONE
WITH THAT THING?

194
00:13:49,329 --> 00:13:51,262
ABOUT.

195
00:13:51,331 --> 00:13:53,797
JUST MAKE SURE IT WORKS.

196
00:13:55,434 --> 00:13:58,102
- IT'LL WORK.
- IT BETTER.

197
00:13:58,171 --> 00:14:02,039
<i> WE'RE GONNA MAKE THIS DAMN</i>
<i> UNITY RALLY A WAKE-UP CALL.</i>

198
00:14:02,108 --> 00:14:05,509
GENERAL SAYS THAT WHEN THE BLOOD
OF ALL THEM SONS OF CAIN...

199
00:14:05,578 --> 00:14:10,615
FLOWS THROUGH THE GUTTERS,
OUR PEOPLE WILL UNITE.

200
00:14:10,683 --> 00:14:13,184
<i>SEE GOD'S WILL TO EXTERMINATE</i>
<i>ALL THE PARASITES...</i>

201
00:14:13,252 --> 00:14:15,252
WHO ARE SUCKING THE LIFE
OUT OF THIS COUNTRY.

202
00:14:15,321 --> 00:14:19,957
- AMEN, BROTHER. AMEN.
- AMEN.

203
00:14:20,026 --> 00:14:24,395
<i>[ Martin Luther King ]</i>
<i>TRANSFORMED INTO AN OASIS</i>
<i>OF FREEDOM AND JUSTICE.</i>

204
00:14:24,464 --> 00:14:28,132
I HAVE A DREAM!
[ Applause ]

205
00:14:28,201 --> 00:14:30,568
THAT MY FOUR
LITTLE CHILDREN--
[ Continues ]

206
00:14:30,636 --> 00:14:33,938
WHY DO PEOPLE HATE
OTHER PEOPLE BECAUSE
OF THE COLOR OF THEIR SKIN?

207
00:14:34,007 --> 00:14:36,674
I DON'T KNOW, JAROD.
IT'S CALLED RACISM.

208
00:14:36,742 --> 00:14:39,677
IT'S IMPORTANT THAT YOU LEARN
WHAT'S WRONG IN THE WORLD...

209
00:14:39,746 --> 00:14:41,912
AS WELL AS WHAT'S RIGHT.

210
00:14:41,981 --> 00:14:44,648
I HAVE A DREAM
THAT ONE DAY--

211
00:14:44,717 --> 00:14:47,318
ARE THEY TAUGHT TO DO THIS?

212
00:14:47,387 --> 00:14:50,254
IN SOME WAYS, YES.

213
00:14:50,322 --> 00:14:54,625
JAROD, THERE IS NO SIMPLE
SOLUTION TO RACISM.

214
00:14:54,694 --> 00:14:56,994
BUT THERE IS.
STOP HATING.

215
00:14:57,063 --> 00:14:59,796
IT TAKES TIME AND COMPASSION.

216
00:14:59,865 --> 00:15:01,932
<i>DO YOU UNDERSTAND</i>
<i>THIS, JAROD?</i>

217
00:15:02,001 --> 00:15:04,602
<i>[ Martin Luther King Continues ]</i>

218
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:09,607
I UNDERSTAND IT,
BUT I CAN'T ACCEPT IT.
<i>I HAVE A DREAM--</i>

219
00:15:09,675 --> 00:15:13,244
WHAT'S THE MATTER
WITH YOU, BOY? YOU LOOK
LIKE YOU SEEN A GHOST.

220
00:15:13,313 --> 00:15:17,148
NO, BROTHER.
JUST SEEIN' THE LIGHT.

221
00:15:18,451 --> 00:15:21,519
THERE. IT'S FINISHED.

222
00:15:21,588 --> 00:15:24,855
WHEN WE PULL THIS OFF,
YOU'RE GONNA SCORE BIG
POINTS WITH THE GENERAL.

223
00:15:24,924 --> 00:15:27,992
I'M GONNA TAKE THIS INTO TOWN,

224
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:31,162
MAKE SURE IT'S ALL
IN PLACE FOR TOMORROW.

225
00:15:31,231 --> 00:15:33,197
<i> [ Door Opens ]</i>
<i> [ Man ]</i>
<i> I DON'T THINK SO.</i>

226
00:15:33,266 --> 00:15:36,667
<i>[ Door Closes ]</i>
<i> NOBODY'S GOIN' INTO TOWN</i>
<i> TILL THE GENERAL ARRIVES.</i>

227
00:15:36,735 --> 00:15:39,036
I DON'T WANNA MAKE
ANYBODY SUSPICIOUS.

228
00:15:39,105 --> 00:15:41,272
I'LL TAKE CARE OF THIS
FROM NOW ON.

229
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:44,208
YOU WANT SOMETHIN' TO DO,
FINISH RELOADIN'
THOSE SHOTGUN SHELLS.

230
00:15:44,277 --> 00:15:48,112
NOW, WAIT A MINUTE.
THE PLAN WAS THAT I WOULD SET
ANY EXPLOSIVES THAT WE USED.

231
00:15:48,181 --> 00:15:51,015
WELL, THE PLAN CHANGED,
HOTSHOT.

232
00:15:51,084 --> 00:15:53,216
GENERAL'S ORDERS.

233
00:15:59,225 --> 00:16:01,225
HE WANTS THIS SET SPECIAL.

234
00:16:06,066 --> 00:16:10,233
HE WANTS THE PREACHER'S
GIRLS TO BE THE MESSAGE.

235
00:16:15,341 --> 00:16:17,408
HE WANTS US TO KILL THEM?

236
00:16:17,477 --> 00:16:22,279
<i> YEP. HE'S GONNA PUT AN END</i>
<i> TO THIS UNITY CRAP</i>
<i> ONCE AND FOR ALL.</i>

237
00:16:30,023 --> 00:16:33,958
<i>[ Sydney ]</i>
<i>I HAVE TRIED EVERY POSSIBLE</i>
<i>AVENUE TO CONTACT JAROD.</i>

238
00:16:34,027 --> 00:16:37,795
-<i> NO RESPONSE.</i>
- SYDNEY, I THINK ANGELO'S
ON TO SOMETHING.

239
00:16:37,863 --> 00:16:40,465
[ Gun Clicking ]

240
00:16:40,533 --> 00:16:42,600
I HOPE HE DOESN'T FIND
THE BULLETS.

241
00:16:42,669 --> 00:16:45,936
THE GUN BELONGED
TO A MID-LEVEL THUG--
A JOEY MELINO.

242
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:48,572
KILLED AN UNDERCOVER COP.
JAROD SENT HIM AWAY.

243
00:16:48,641 --> 00:16:51,709
<i>WORD FROM PRISON IS,</i>
<i>JOEY'S NOT TOO HAPPY ABOUT IT.</i>

244
00:16:51,778 --> 00:16:54,011
MAYBE HE'S PAYING SOMEONE
TO KILL JAROD.

245
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:57,581
-<i> [ Gun Clicks ]</i>
- [ Screaming ]

246
00:17:00,319 --> 00:17:02,320
[ Screaming ]
ANGELO, WHAT IS IT?

247
00:17:02,388 --> 00:17:07,058
THERE IS DANGER! DEATH! HATE!
HATE GETTING CLOSER TO JAROD!

248
00:17:15,234 --> 00:17:17,735
OH!
[ Uncocks ]

249
00:17:18,971 --> 00:17:20,972
<i>[ Sighs ]</i>

250
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:25,643
JAROD DOESN'T WANT HATE.
DOESN'T WANT TO KILL.

251
00:17:27,446 --> 00:17:30,815
BUT SOMEONE WANTS
TO KILL JAROD!

252
00:17:32,285 --> 00:17:37,554
DID YOU REALLY THINK
I WOULDN'T FIND OUT
WHO YOU ARE? HUH?

253
00:17:38,791 --> 00:17:41,425
<i> JAROD!</i>

254
00:17:45,331 --> 00:17:48,132
[ Shuddering ]

255
00:17:52,104 --> 00:17:55,239
YOU'RE A DEAD MAN, JAROD!
YOU HEAR ME? YOU'RE DEAD!

256
00:17:55,308 --> 00:17:57,141
OOH, YOU NEED TO CHILL OUT.

257
00:17:57,209 --> 00:18:00,644
LISTEN, JAROD, I'LL
GIVE YOU ANYTHING YOU WANT.

258
00:18:00,713 --> 00:18:02,546
- SEE YA.
- JAROD, NO!

259
00:18:02,615 --> 00:18:04,882
<i>LET US OUT!</i>
<i>HE'S DEAD! HE'S DEAD!</i>

260
00:18:04,951 --> 00:18:08,786
<i>YOU'RE DEAD!</i>
<i> YOU'RE DEAD!</i>
[ Gasps, Whimpering ]

261
00:18:08,855 --> 00:18:11,689
ANGELO, IS IT JOEY?

262
00:18:11,757 --> 00:18:15,893
NO, NOT-- NOT JOEY!
SOMEONE HATES JAROD MORE.

263
00:18:15,962 --> 00:18:19,730
<i> HATES OTHERS.</i>
<i> WE MUST FIND SOON.</i>

264
00:18:19,799 --> 00:18:23,501
THIS IS GOING NOWHERE.
<i> JAROD WILL DIE!</i>

265
00:18:23,569 --> 00:18:25,869
PATIENCE, PARKER.

266
00:18:25,938 --> 00:18:28,139
ANGELO IS NARROWING DOWN
THE SUSPECTS.

267
00:18:28,208 --> 00:18:31,708
<i> MUST FIND SOON,</i>
<i> OR JAROD WILL DIE.</i>

268
00:18:31,777 --> 00:18:34,645
WE DON'T HAVE TIME
TO BE PATIENT.

269
00:18:46,593 --> 00:18:50,026
<i>FINISH THEM SHELLS,</i>
<i>JAROD. WE NEED ANOTHER</i>
<i>LOSER AT THE TABLE.</i>

270
00:18:50,095 --> 00:18:52,363
[ Laughing ]

271
00:18:52,431 --> 00:18:54,898
YOU BEEN CHEATIN'. YOU GOTTA
GIVE ME A CHANCE TO WIN.

272
00:18:54,967 --> 00:18:57,334
-<i> EVERYBODY'S CHEATIN', DONNY.</i>
- WHO'S CHEATIN'?

273
00:18:57,403 --> 00:18:59,336
DELBERT.
YEAH!

274
00:18:59,405 --> 00:19:03,373
WHAT YOU GOT?
WHAT YOU GOT?
[ Laughing ]

275
00:19:03,442 --> 00:19:05,676
LET'S MOVE ALONG, MAN.
<i> NO, NO, NO, NO.</i>

276
00:19:05,745 --> 00:19:09,714
<i> TWO PAIR. TWO PAIR.</i>
<i> TWO 10s, TWO SIXES,</i>
<i> AND ALL MINE, PARTNER.</i>

277
00:19:09,782 --> 00:19:12,249
[ Laughing ]

278
00:19:12,318 --> 00:19:15,619
<i>[ Chattering Continues ]</i>

279
00:19:15,688 --> 00:19:19,056
<i>[ Donny ]</i>
<i>LOOK. FIVE. TWO ACES.</i>
<i>A PAIR OF ACES.</i>

280
00:19:19,124 --> 00:19:22,426
<i>JUST GIVE ME THREE MORE.</i>

281
00:19:22,495 --> 00:19:24,528
<i>ATTABOY.</i>
<i>[ Laughs ]</i>

282
00:19:28,367 --> 00:19:31,301
-<i> [ Indistinct Chattering ]</i>
- LOOK AT THAT THING.

283
00:19:31,370 --> 00:19:34,438
<i>[ Chattering Continues ]</i>

284
00:19:52,725 --> 00:19:56,393
<i>[ Rifle cocks ]</i>
<i>GOIN' SOMEWHERE?</i>

285
00:19:56,462 --> 00:20:01,398
YEAH. TO GET
A LITTLE BLACK POWDER
TO PACK AROUND THE C-4.

286
00:20:01,467 --> 00:20:04,100
I THOUGHT IT MIGHT GIVE
MORE IMPACT VISUALLY.

287
00:20:04,169 --> 00:20:06,470
GENERAL WANTS TO USE NAPALM.

288
00:20:06,539 --> 00:20:09,740
NAPALM? BUT THAT
WASN'T PART--
NAH, NO BUTS.

289
00:20:09,809 --> 00:20:14,011
HIS PLAN, HIS CAUSE--
WE DO THINGS HIS WAY.

290
00:20:15,915 --> 00:20:18,115
YOU GOT A PROBLEM WITH THAT?

291
00:20:18,184 --> 00:20:20,284
HELL, NO.
I'M A BELIEVER.

292
00:20:20,352 --> 00:20:22,586
I JUST LIKE TO KNOW
WHAT'S GOIN' ON. THAT'S ALL.

293
00:20:22,655 --> 00:20:25,856
AND RIGHT NOW WHAT'S GOIN' ON
IS YOU'RE STAYIN' HERE.

294
00:20:25,925 --> 00:20:27,858
YES--
GENERAL'S ORDERS.

295
00:20:27,927 --> 00:20:29,860
YES, SIR.
LUKE.

296
00:20:29,929 --> 00:20:33,363
WHAT?
YOU GOT ANOTHER MESSAGE
FROM THE GENERAL.

297
00:20:33,433 --> 00:20:36,700
THERE A PROBLEM?
AS A MATTER OF FACT,
THERE IS.

298
00:20:36,769 --> 00:20:39,936
HE HAS WORD ONE OF US ISN'T
EXACTLY WHO WE CLAIM TO BE.

299
00:20:40,005 --> 00:20:42,840
<i>SOUNDS LIKE ONE OF US</i>
<i>IS A TRAITOR.</i>

300
00:20:42,909 --> 00:20:46,777
<i>GENERAL SAID TO TELL YOU</i>
<i>NO ONE LEAVES TILL HE GETS HERE.</i>

301
00:20:46,845 --> 00:20:49,146
ALL RIGHT.

302
00:20:49,215 --> 00:20:53,850
<i>YOU BOYS GET BACK IN THE HOUSE.</i>
<i>WE'LL SORT THIS OUT</i>
<i>WHEN THE GENERAL SHOWS UP.</i>

303
00:20:57,390 --> 00:21:00,124
HEY.
[ Whistles ]

304
00:21:14,841 --> 00:21:17,908
<i> GOD BLESS KATI AND DADDY.</i>

305
00:21:17,977 --> 00:21:21,378
AND GOD BLESS MOMMA
UP IN HEAVEN. AMEN.

306
00:21:21,447 --> 00:21:23,881
AMEN.
AMEN.

307
00:21:23,950 --> 00:21:26,416
ALL RIGHT, YOU TWO.
TIME FOR BED.

308
00:21:26,485 --> 00:21:29,854
DADDY'S ANGELS
GOT TO REST THOSE VOICES
FOR THE RALLY TOMORROW.

309
00:21:34,893 --> 00:21:37,728
WHY DO THOSE PEOPLE
HATE US?

310
00:21:37,797 --> 00:21:39,730
WHAT DID WE DO?

311
00:21:42,935 --> 00:21:45,368
HERE. SIT DOWN.
COME HERE, BABY.

312
00:21:45,437 --> 00:21:48,371
[ Sighs ]
LISTEN.

313
00:21:48,441 --> 00:21:51,374
YOU DIDN'T DO ANYTHING WRONG.
YOU HEAR ME, SWEETHEART?

314
00:21:51,444 --> 00:21:54,611
YOU DID NOTHING AT ALL.

315
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:58,782
PEOPLE HATE...
'CAUSE THEY'RE AFRAID.

316
00:21:58,851 --> 00:22:02,152
THEY'RE AFRAID OF THINGS
THAT THEY DON'T KNOW.

317
00:22:02,220 --> 00:22:04,554
THINGS THAT
THEY DON'T UNDERSTAND.

318
00:22:04,623 --> 00:22:07,858
THAT'S WHY THIS RALLY
IS SO IMPORTANT.

319
00:22:07,927 --> 00:22:09,860
UNDERSTAND?
MM-HMM.

320
00:22:09,929 --> 00:22:11,862
YOU SURE?
YES.

321
00:22:11,931 --> 00:22:14,131
GOOD. ALL RIGHT.
LET'S GET TO BED.

322
00:22:14,199 --> 00:22:16,867
GET SOME SLEEP, AND WE'LL
SEE YOU IN THE MORNING.
ALL RIGHT.

323
00:22:16,936 --> 00:22:19,804
MM. NIGHT. UH-OH.
GOT IT? DADDY GOT IT.

324
00:22:19,872 --> 00:22:22,172
MM. LOVE YOU.

325
00:22:24,543 --> 00:22:27,277
DADDY?

326
00:22:27,346 --> 00:22:30,113
CAN YOU PLEASE
CLOSE THE WINDOW?

327
00:22:32,951 --> 00:22:34,885
SURE, SWEETHEART.

328
00:22:38,491 --> 00:22:41,425
AND LOCK IT.

329
00:22:46,331 --> 00:22:49,266
THERE. IT'S LOCKED.

330
00:22:57,543 --> 00:23:00,177
- GOOD NIGHT.
- [ Both ] GOOD NIGHT.

331
00:23:06,018 --> 00:23:08,485
[ Exhales ]

332
00:23:26,739 --> 00:23:29,673
<i>ANY WORD ON JAROD?</i>

333
00:23:31,878 --> 00:23:35,012
- LOOKS LIKE SATURDAY NIGHT
AT YOUR HOUSE, BROOTS.
- HUH?

334
00:23:35,081 --> 00:23:38,281
ANGELO'S TRYING TO EMPATH
CAPTAIN ROBERT SAUNDERS.

335
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:42,386
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>HE'S THE ONE SERVING 20 TO LIFE</i>
<i>AT LEAVENWORTH, THANKS TO JAROD.</i>

336
00:23:42,454 --> 00:23:46,823
<i> CAPTAIN ROBERT SAUNDERS.</i>
<i> TEXTBOOK SOCIOPATH.</i>

337
00:23:46,892 --> 00:23:50,060
AS WELL AS A CONVICTED
RAPIST AND MURDERER.

338
00:23:50,129 --> 00:23:52,362
<i> HE CERTAINLY FITS</i>
<i> THE PROFILE.</i>

339
00:23:52,431 --> 00:23:55,065
AND HE'S ON RECORD AS HAVING
SWORN TO GET BACK AT JAROD.

340
00:23:55,134 --> 00:23:57,300
JAROD SURE KNOWS HOW TO PICK
HIS ENEMIES, DOESN'T HE?

341
00:23:57,370 --> 00:24:00,203
- YES, HE HAS A PENCHANT
FOR PISSING PEOPLE OFF.
- [ Angelo Screams ]

342
00:24:01,807 --> 00:24:03,740
[ Groans ]

343
00:24:05,844 --> 00:24:08,645
SAUNDERS!

344
00:24:08,714 --> 00:24:13,550
HATES JAROD!

345
00:24:13,618 --> 00:24:16,186
WANTS TO HURT JAROD!

346
00:24:16,255 --> 00:24:19,590
WANTS TO HURT JAROD!

347
00:24:19,659 --> 00:24:22,159
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>WHAT'S THE MATTER, SAUNDERS?</i>
<i>YOU LOOK SCARED.</i>

348
00:24:22,227 --> 00:24:25,061
- WHO'S IN HERE?
- JUST DEMONS IN YOUR MIND.

349
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:27,898
STEVENS, IS THAT YOU?
HEY, THIS IS CRAZY!

350
00:24:27,967 --> 00:24:33,503
WELL, GOTTA GO NOW.
HAVE FUN IN YOUR OWN
PRIVATE LITTLE... HELL.

351
00:24:33,572 --> 00:24:37,574
DON'T LEAVE! COME ON!
LET ME OUT!
[ Echoing ]

352
00:24:37,643 --> 00:24:40,877
[ Screaming ]

353
00:24:40,946 --> 00:24:46,716
[ Grunts ]
SAUNDERS HATES JAROD,
BUT... NOT HIM.

354
00:24:46,785 --> 00:24:49,153
SOMEONE ELSE
HATES JAROD MORE.

355
00:24:49,221 --> 00:24:52,088
IT'S HARD TO IMAGINE
IT COULD GET MUCH WORSE.

356
00:24:52,157 --> 00:24:57,261
[ Panting ]
BROOTS! HURRY!

357
00:24:57,330 --> 00:24:59,296
THERE'S NO TIME
LEFT FOR JAROD!

358
00:24:59,365 --> 00:25:01,598
ANGELO, CALM DOWN!
I'VE NEVER SEEN HIM LIKE THIS.

359
00:25:01,667 --> 00:25:05,869
CAN'T CALM DOWN!
[ Screaming ]

360
00:25:05,938 --> 00:25:09,239
HATES JAROD! HATES JAROD!

361
00:25:13,512 --> 00:25:17,247
[ Yells ]
HATES MISS PARKER TOO!

362
00:25:38,103 --> 00:25:40,137
[ Dog Barking ]

363
00:25:40,205 --> 00:25:42,940
<i>[ Barking Continues ]</i>

364
00:25:49,247 --> 00:25:51,514
ALL RIGHT. HE'S HERE.

365
00:25:58,390 --> 00:26:02,158
JAROD, GET THEM DAMN
BEER BOTTLES OUTTA HERE.

366
00:26:06,831 --> 00:26:08,932
<i>[ Dog Continues Barking ]</i>

367
00:26:26,418 --> 00:26:30,220
GENERAL,
WE'RE GLAD YOU'RE HERE.

368
00:26:30,289 --> 00:26:31,955
GENERAL.

369
00:26:33,559 --> 00:26:35,625
SIR.

370
00:26:35,694 --> 00:26:37,961
EVERYTHING'S READY
FOR TOMORROW, SIR. WE'RE
JUST WAITIN' ON YOUR WORD.

371
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:40,697
<i> JUST LIKE YOU ORDERED,</i>
<i> NONE OF US HAVE LEFT.</i>

372
00:26:40,766 --> 00:26:43,734
WE'RE ALL HERE
TO HELP YOU FIGURE OUT
WHO THE TRAITOR IS, SIR.

373
00:26:47,373 --> 00:26:50,407
WELL, THAT WON'T
BE NECESSARY,

374
00:26:50,475 --> 00:26:52,409
<i> WILL IT, JAROD?</i>

375
00:26:54,713 --> 00:26:57,013
[ Screams ]

376
00:26:57,082 --> 00:26:59,950
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?
YOU GONNA STAND THERE
OR CUT ME OUT OF THIS?

377
00:27:00,018 --> 00:27:02,552
I SPENT A LONG TIME
MAKING THAT THING.

378
00:27:02,621 --> 00:27:05,989
YOU CUT ME OUTTA THIS NOW,
OR I'LL BLOW YOU AWAY.
<i> [ Gun Clicking ]</i>

379
00:27:06,058 --> 00:27:10,527
<i>GUESS YOUR CLIP'S EMPTY.</i>
<i>GOTTA GO. HURRICANE'S COMIN'</i>
<i>RIGHT THROUGH HERE.</i>

380
00:27:10,596 --> 00:27:13,030
YOU'RE DEAD! YOU'RE DEAD,
YOU SON OF A--

381
00:27:15,234 --> 00:27:17,834
MATTER OF FACT, WE GO BACK
A LONG WAY, DON'T WE?

382
00:27:17,903 --> 00:27:21,171
LAST TIME WE WERE TOGETHER,
THERE WAS A HURRICANE
BLOWIN'.

383
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:23,173
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHIN'.

384
00:27:23,242 --> 00:27:27,177
THAT STORM AIN'T GOT
HALF THE FURY THAT I GOT
LEFT IN ME RIGHT NOW.

385
00:27:31,617 --> 00:27:37,421
- [ Jarod Grunting ]
- [ Men Cheering ]

386
00:27:37,490 --> 00:27:39,556
- TRAITOR!
- [ Men Shouting ]

387
00:27:39,625 --> 00:27:42,126
- YEAH, GET HIM! GET HIM!
- [ Men Cheering ]

388
00:27:46,665 --> 00:27:49,032
GENTLEMEN,
WE'RE BACK ON SCHEDULE.

389
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:52,970
<i> BARTLETT'S THE GUY THAT</i>
<i> TRIED TO KILL JAROD...</i>
<i> AND YOU.</i>

390
00:27:53,038 --> 00:27:54,972
AND ALMOST SUCCEEDED.

391
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:57,407
I HAD TRACKED JAROD TO
THE MIDDLE OF THE EVERGLADES...

392
00:27:57,476 --> 00:28:00,176
WHERE WE WERE TRAPPED
TOGETHER IN A HURRICANE.

393
00:28:00,245 --> 00:28:02,980
SO THAT'S THE NET
JAROD USED TO CAPTURE HIM.

394
00:28:03,048 --> 00:28:05,916
TOOK MORE THAN A NET TO HOLD
AN ANIMAL LIKE BARTLETT.

395
00:28:05,985 --> 00:28:09,887
[ Growling ]

396
00:28:12,157 --> 00:28:14,157
<i> [ Gunshot ]</i>

397
00:28:14,226 --> 00:28:17,161
<i> HONEY, I'M HOME.</i>

398
00:28:20,065 --> 00:28:24,134
<i> BARTLETT, ANGELO.</i>
<i> IS HE THE ONE WHO'S</i>
<i> GOING TO KILL JAROD?</i>

399
00:28:24,203 --> 00:28:26,736
BARTLETT.
MUST STOP BARTLETT.

400
00:28:26,805 --> 00:28:29,473
BARTLETT HATES JAROD.
HATES EVERYONE.

401
00:28:29,541 --> 00:28:32,509
<i>BARTLETT WANTS TO KILL.</i>
<i>WANTS TO KILL JAROD.</i>

402
00:28:32,577 --> 00:28:36,680
SYDNEY, HELP JAROD NOW.
PARKER, WE HAVE
TO DO SOMETHING.

403
00:28:36,748 --> 00:28:38,815
BROOTS, CALL THE
FLORIDA BUREAU OF PRISONS.

404
00:28:38,883 --> 00:28:41,684
- FIND OUT IF BARTLETT
IS STILL IN CUSTODY.
- OKAY.

405
00:28:41,753 --> 00:28:46,122
BARTLETT IS
A RACIST SLEAZEBAG...

406
00:28:46,191 --> 00:28:49,492
<i>WHO WOULD KILL HIS OWN MOTHER.</i>

407
00:28:49,561 --> 00:28:51,494
SYD, WE HAVE TO FIND HIM.

408
00:28:51,564 --> 00:28:54,864
IF BARTLETT FINDS JAROD
FIRST, HE WILL KILL HIM.

409
00:28:58,937 --> 00:29:01,838
AND RUIN MY CHANCE.

410
00:29:03,209 --> 00:29:05,842
<i>[ Gasps, Sighs ]</i>

411
00:29:05,911 --> 00:29:08,178
LET'S JUST PRAY
WE'RE NOT TOO LATE.

412
00:29:12,684 --> 00:29:15,485
<i> JAROD, THE LORD WORKS</i>
<i> IN MYSTERIOUS WAYS.</i>

413
00:29:15,554 --> 00:29:17,654
SEE, YOU WERE HIS INSTRUMENT
TO HAVE ME THROWN INTO JAIL...

414
00:29:17,723 --> 00:29:20,523
<i> WHERE I COULD COME TO SEE</i>
<i> HIS PURPOSE IN MY LIFE.</i>

415
00:29:20,592 --> 00:29:23,826
AND THEN THROUGH HIS DIVINE
PROVIDENCE, I WAS SET FREE...

416
00:29:23,895 --> 00:29:26,963
SO THAT I COULD UNITE MY PEOPLE
AND CLEANSE THIS COUNTRY.

417
00:29:27,032 --> 00:29:29,566
AND NOW HERE YOU ARE,
DROPPED RIGHT IN MY LAP.

418
00:29:29,634 --> 00:29:32,969
- MANNA FROM HEAVEN.
- YOU'RE SICK, BARTLETT.

419
00:29:33,038 --> 00:29:37,808
<i>YOU'RE SO CONSUMED WITH HATE,</i>
<i>YOU'LL DESTROY YOURSELF</i>
<i>AND EVERYONE AROUND YOU.</i>

420
00:29:39,144 --> 00:29:42,012
- NO, JAROD. I'M NOT SICK.
- [ Jarod Groans ]

421
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:46,549
MISUNDERSTOOD, YES.
PERSECUTED LIKE THE PROPHETS
OF OLD, YES. BUT NOT SICK.

422
00:29:46,618 --> 00:29:50,553
- [ Grunts, Groans ]
- WHAT DO WE DO WITH HIM?

423
00:29:50,622 --> 00:29:53,089
I'LL TAKE HIM OUT IN THE WOODS
AND SEND HIM TO HIS JUDGMENT.

424
00:29:53,158 --> 00:29:55,692
[ Whimpers ]

425
00:29:55,761 --> 00:29:59,296
[ Grunting ]
YOU DON'T NEED TO DIRTY
YOUR HANDS WITH THIS.

426
00:29:59,364 --> 00:30:03,700
LET ME DO IT.
IT'D BE MY HONOR TO TAKE
THIS JUDAS TO HIS JUSTICE.

427
00:30:11,810 --> 00:30:14,277
A TRUE APOSTLE.

428
00:30:16,014 --> 00:30:18,881
DO IT DOWN BY THE CREEK AND
JUST LEAVE HIS BODY THERE.

429
00:30:18,950 --> 00:30:21,151
DUST TO DUST.

430
00:30:21,219 --> 00:30:23,954
WE HAVE THINGS TO DO
FOR THE UNITY RALLY
TOMORROW, DON'T WE?

431
00:30:24,022 --> 00:30:27,390
THERE ARE GONNA BE
A LOT OF PEOPLE SINGING
THE BLUES TOMORROW.

432
00:30:27,458 --> 00:30:31,761
<i> GET HIM OUTTA HERE.</i>
COME ON. COME ON.

433
00:30:31,830 --> 00:30:34,363
LET'S GO.

434
00:30:37,635 --> 00:30:40,269
LET'S GO!
[ Grunts ]

435
00:30:50,649 --> 00:30:53,816
[ Jarod Panting ]

436
00:31:03,028 --> 00:31:05,728
[ Gasping ]

437
00:31:07,766 --> 00:31:09,999
[ Gasps ]

438
00:31:16,541 --> 00:31:18,708
LET'S GO.

439
00:31:18,777 --> 00:31:22,411
GO ON! GET DOWN!
GET DOWN ON YOUR KNEES!

440
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:26,449
[ Panting ]
YOU CAN'T DO THIS!

441
00:31:31,990 --> 00:31:34,123
<i>[ Gunshot ]</i>

442
00:31:47,272 --> 00:31:50,373
<i> [ Panting Continues ]</i>

443
00:31:50,442 --> 00:31:53,743
I HOPE I DIDN'T
SCARE YA TOO BAD.

444
00:31:53,812 --> 00:31:57,513
WELL, I GOTTA CHECK MY PANTS.
BUT I'M STILL ALIVE.

445
00:31:57,582 --> 00:32:00,216
I'M UNDERCOVER TOO.
GEORGIA STATE POLICE.

446
00:32:00,285 --> 00:32:02,385
A.T.F., FEDERAL TASK FORCE.

447
00:32:02,454 --> 00:32:04,887
WE'VE BEEN AFTER BARTLETT
EVER SINCE HIS CONVICTION
FOR MURDER...

448
00:32:04,956 --> 00:32:07,357
AND CIVIL RIGHTS VIOLATIONS
WERE OVERTURNED.

449
00:32:07,426 --> 00:32:10,226
SOME FED POPPED HIM FOR THOSE.
MY GUESS IS THAT WAS YOU.

450
00:32:10,295 --> 00:32:12,228
GUILTY.

451
00:32:12,297 --> 00:32:15,531
I HAD NO IDEA
HE'D BEEN RELEASED.
DO YOU HAVE A PLAN?

452
00:32:15,600 --> 00:32:18,968
NO, BARTLETT'S CHANGING
EVERYTHING. I'M COMPLETELY
CUT OFF FROM THE OUTSIDE.

453
00:32:19,036 --> 00:32:22,639
LOOK, WE GO BACK IN THERE
RIGHT NOW, WE CAN POP HIM
FOR CONSPIRACY.

454
00:32:22,707 --> 00:32:26,175
NO. WE CATCH HIM IN THE ACT
OF SETTING THOSE EXPLOSIVES,
WE CAN PUT HIM AWAY FOR LIFE.

455
00:32:26,244 --> 00:32:30,346
IF WE DON'T STOP HIM,
HE'S GONNA KILL
PASTOR JONES'S LITTLE GIRLS.

456
00:32:44,328 --> 00:32:49,999
HERE. HERE.
[ Panting ]

457
00:32:50,068 --> 00:32:53,469
YOU GO BACK IN THERE.
YOU KEEP HIM COMPANY.

458
00:32:53,538 --> 00:32:57,940
I'LL THINK OF SOMETHING.
AND, UH, GOOD LUCK.

459
00:32:58,009 --> 00:33:00,409
GOOD LUCK.

460
00:33:02,814 --> 00:33:06,282
<i> HE DIDN'T BEG... MUCH.</i>

461
00:33:06,351 --> 00:33:09,452
[ Men Laughing ]

462
00:33:09,521 --> 00:33:13,990
WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD.
TAKES SOME OF THE FUN OUT OF IT.

463
00:33:24,502 --> 00:33:27,670
I SHOULD'VE KNOWN. JAROD
CROSSED THE DETONATOR WIRES.

464
00:33:27,739 --> 00:33:30,873
THIS THING
WOULD'VE NEVER GONE OFF.

465
00:33:33,945 --> 00:33:36,579
WELL, LOOK AT THAT.
AIN'T THAT PRETTY?

466
00:33:39,351 --> 00:33:41,784
A LITTLE C-4 AND NAPALM--

467
00:33:41,853 --> 00:33:43,953
THAT OUGHTA MAKE
QUITE A LITTLE STATEMENT.

468
00:33:44,022 --> 00:33:46,923
YES, SIR, IT WILL.
I'LL JUST RUN THAT
INTO TOWN.

469
00:33:46,992 --> 00:33:49,191
YOU TELL ME WHERE YOU
WANT ME TO PLACE IT.

470
00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:53,896
NO. THIS IS MY VISION.
MY CALLING.

471
00:33:53,965 --> 00:33:56,232
- THEN WE'LL DO IT TOGETHER.
- I SAID IT WAS MY CALLING.

472
00:33:59,337 --> 00:34:02,571
I DO IT ALONE.

473
00:34:04,175 --> 00:34:07,010
YOU BOYS JUST BE READY
TOMORROW.

474
00:34:07,078 --> 00:34:09,311
BE READY FOR WAR.

475
00:34:13,317 --> 00:34:16,186
<i> [ Door Closes ]</i>

476
00:34:22,227 --> 00:34:24,293
<i>[ Young Sydney ]</i>
<i>I'D LIKE YOU TO MEET</i>
<i>SOMEONE, JAROD.</i>

477
00:34:29,801 --> 00:34:32,835
YOU'RE A GIRL.

478
00:34:32,904 --> 00:34:36,339
- WHY DID YOU SAVE MY LIFE?
- BECAUSE...

479
00:34:36,407 --> 00:34:41,211
I STILL REMEMBER THE LITTLE GIRL
WHO GAVE ME MY FIRST KISS.

480
00:34:56,761 --> 00:35:00,396
I FOUND OUT SOMETHING
ON BARTLETT. HE'S BEEN
RELEASED FROM PRISON.

481
00:35:00,465 --> 00:35:03,199
LET ME GUESS.
HIS CONVICTION WAS OVERTURNED
ON A TECHNICALITY.

482
00:35:03,268 --> 00:35:08,037
EXACTLY. BUT WHILE HE WAS
IN PRISON, HE STARTED A VIOLENT
WHITE SUPREMACIST GROUP.

483
00:35:08,106 --> 00:35:10,039
<i> AND?</i>
AND RUMOR IS
HE'S IN GEORGIA...

484
00:35:10,108 --> 00:35:13,476
AND HE'S ORGANIZED
A MARCH IN OPPOSITION
TO A UNITY RALLY TOMORROW.

485
00:35:13,544 --> 00:35:15,845
THEN LET'S STOP
THE SON OF A BITCH.
OKAY.

486
00:35:15,914 --> 00:35:18,647
AND GET JAROD.

487
00:35:53,651 --> 00:35:56,753
[ Muttering Prayer ]

488
00:35:58,156 --> 00:36:01,924
<i>[ Piano Keys Slamming ]</i>

489
00:36:01,993 --> 00:36:04,594
- HERE TO REPENT, BROTHER!
- JAROD?

490
00:36:04,663 --> 00:36:08,631
- NOW WHO'S SINGING THE BLUES?
- I'M SO SICK TO DEATH OF YOU!

491
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:10,700
YOU HAVE MORE LIVES
THAN A BARNYARD CAT.

492
00:36:10,769 --> 00:36:13,569
<i> BUT THIS IS GONNA BE</i>
<i> YOUR LAST ONE.</i>

493
00:36:13,638 --> 00:36:17,773
YOU WEREN'T ABLE TO TAKE
THE ROUNDS OUT OF MY CLIP
THIS TIME.

494
00:36:23,782 --> 00:36:25,914
WELL, I AM SORRY
TO DISAPPOINT YOU,

495
00:36:25,983 --> 00:36:28,951
BUT GUESS WHO RELOADED
THOSE SHELLS?

496
00:36:29,019 --> 00:36:30,886
I MUST HAVE FORGOT
TO PUT SHOT IN THEM.

497
00:36:30,955 --> 00:36:33,322
YOU SON OF A BITCH!
[ Grunts ]

498
00:36:33,391 --> 00:36:36,292
OH, BY THE WAY,
I OWE YOU THIS ONE.

499
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:38,795
[ Grunts ]

500
00:36:38,863 --> 00:36:40,796
<i> [ Drops Bat ]</i>
[ Sighs ]

501
00:36:48,072 --> 00:36:50,973
<i> [ Jarod ]</i>
<i> OH, BARTLETT?</i>

502
00:36:51,042 --> 00:36:53,676
BARTLETT?

503
00:36:54,812 --> 00:36:57,813
- WAKE UP!
- [ Sighs ]

504
00:37:01,452 --> 00:37:04,854
JAROD, WHAT
THE HELL IS THIS?

505
00:37:04,922 --> 00:37:07,323
THINK OF IT
AS YOUR CROSS TO BEAR.

506
00:37:07,392 --> 00:37:10,493
<i>AND SINCE YOU SO ENJOY</i>
<i>BURNING CROSSES...</i>

507
00:37:10,562 --> 00:37:12,995
AND TERRORIZING
INNOCENT FAMILIES,

508
00:37:13,064 --> 00:37:16,465
<i>I THOUGHT IT MIGHT BE FUN</i>
<i>FOR</i> YOU<i> TO EXPERIENCE</i>
<i>TERROR FOR ONCE.</i>

509
00:37:16,534 --> 00:37:19,135
<i>LIKE YOU WERE GOING TO DO</i>
<i>TO THOSE TWO INNOCENT</i>
<i>LITTLE GIRLS!</i>

510
00:37:19,203 --> 00:37:22,472
I WASN'T GONNA SCARE 'EM.
I WAS GONNA KILL 'EM!
[ Laughs ]

511
00:37:24,876 --> 00:37:27,309
DON'T MAKE ME LAUGH.

512
00:37:27,378 --> 00:37:30,212
NOW, WE'VE BEEN THROUGH THIS
BEFORE, JAROD.

513
00:37:30,281 --> 00:37:33,015
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DO ANYTHING.
[ Laughing ]

514
00:37:33,084 --> 00:37:35,985
YOU AIN'T GOT
THE HEART FOR IT.

515
00:37:36,054 --> 00:37:39,388
NOW, THAT BITCH
YOU WERE WITH BEFORE--
SHE COULD DO IT.

516
00:37:41,259 --> 00:37:43,525
<i>YEAH.</i>

517
00:37:43,594 --> 00:37:48,664
WELL, YOU SEE,
IT'S NOT HEART THAT I NEED
TO BURN YOU AT THE STAKE.

518
00:37:51,235 --> 00:37:53,669
IT'S ANOTHER PART
OF MY ANATOMY.

519
00:37:53,738 --> 00:37:56,805
AND LET ME TELL YA,
I GOT THOSE.

520
00:37:56,874 --> 00:37:59,642
[ Grunts ]
YOU'LL NEVER GET AWAY WITH THIS!
I GOT PEOPLE OUT THERE.

521
00:37:59,711 --> 00:38:02,679
LUKE AND THE BOYS.
LUKE! LUKE!

522
00:38:02,747 --> 00:38:04,680
[ Laughs ]
YOU KNOW, SOMETHING, BARTLETT?

523
00:38:04,749 --> 00:38:07,150
YOU'RE NOT AS SMART
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

524
00:38:07,218 --> 00:38:09,518
YOU HAD TWO INFILTRATORS
IN YOUR GROUP.

525
00:38:11,055 --> 00:38:14,490
LUKE WAS AN UNDERCOVER COP
WITH THE GEORGIA STATE POLICE.

526
00:38:14,558 --> 00:38:17,893
THE REST OF YOUR APOSTLES
SHOULD BE IN CUSTODY
JUST ABOUT NOW.

527
00:38:17,962 --> 00:38:22,431
- DAMN YOU! DAMN YOU!
- NO! DAMN YOU!

528
00:38:25,069 --> 00:38:27,770
YOU CAN'T DO THIS!
PLEASE DON'T DO IT!
DON'T DO IT! DON'T!

529
00:38:27,838 --> 00:38:30,540
HELP! I DON'T WANNA DIE!

530
00:38:30,608 --> 00:38:34,677
<i>NO! NO! NO!</i>

531
00:38:34,745 --> 00:38:37,379
<i>DON'T BURN ME ALIVE!</i>
<i>PLEASE!</i>

532
00:38:37,448 --> 00:38:40,950
JAROD, I'M SORRY! PLEASE!
I DON'T WANNA DIE!

533
00:38:41,019 --> 00:38:44,720
<i>JAROD, I'M BEGGING YOU!</i>
<i>PLEASE, NOT LIKE THIS!</i>

534
00:38:47,291 --> 00:38:51,026
GOD! NO! NO!
I DON'T WANNA DIE!

535
00:38:51,095 --> 00:38:53,529
<i>I DON'T WANNA DIE!</i>
<i>SOMEONE HELP ME!</i>

536
00:38:53,598 --> 00:38:57,499
HELP! HELP, JAROD, PLEASE!
I'M SORRY! I'M SO SORRY!

537
00:38:57,568 --> 00:39:01,570
<i>DEAR GOD! PLEASE! NO!</i>

538
00:39:01,639 --> 00:39:07,143
[ Sobbing ]

539
00:39:11,382 --> 00:39:13,882
<i> YOU KNOW SOMETHING?</i>
<i> YOU'RE RIGHT.</i>

540
00:39:13,951 --> 00:39:15,918
I DON'T HAVE
THE HEART TO KILL.

541
00:39:15,987 --> 00:39:18,754
-<i> [ Sirens Wailing ]</i>
- OR THE HATE.

542
00:39:18,823 --> 00:39:21,991
<i>[ Sirens Continue ]</i>
MMM.

543
00:39:24,329 --> 00:39:27,863
HAVE FUN...
ROTTING IN PRISON.

544
00:39:32,771 --> 00:39:35,137
[ Whimpering ]

545
00:39:46,984 --> 00:39:50,419
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪

546
00:39:50,488 --> 00:39:54,890
♪ OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪

547
00:39:54,959 --> 00:39:59,028
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪

548
00:39:59,097 --> 00:40:03,866
♪ LET THE HEALING START ♪

549
00:40:03,934 --> 00:40:08,104
♪ BE BLESSED AND GUIDED ♪

550
00:40:08,172 --> 00:40:12,608
♪ THROUGH ETERNITY ♪

551
00:40:12,676 --> 00:40:17,113
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪

552
00:40:17,181 --> 00:40:21,617
♪ AND BE FREE ♪

553
00:40:21,685 --> 00:40:25,821
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDEN ♪

554
00:40:25,890 --> 00:40:30,026
♪ AND BE FREE ♪

555
00:40:37,268 --> 00:40:41,536
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪</i>

556
00:40:41,606 --> 00:40:44,807
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  LET THE HEALING START ♪</i>

557
00:40:44,876 --> 00:40:49,344
♪ BE BLESSED AND GUIDED
THROUGH ETERNITY ♪

558
00:40:49,414 --> 00:40:52,981
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪

559
00:40:53,050 --> 00:40:56,985
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS
AND BE FREE ♪

560
00:40:57,054 --> 00:40:59,321
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪

561
00:40:59,390 --> 00:41:02,258
♪ AND BE FREE ♪

562
00:41:04,962 --> 00:41:09,064
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

563
00:41:09,133 --> 00:41:13,135
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪</i>

564
00:41:13,204 --> 00:41:16,906
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪

565
00:41:16,974 --> 00:41:20,909
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS
AND YOU WILL BE FREE ♪

566
00:41:20,978 --> 00:41:25,414
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

567
00:41:25,483 --> 00:41:29,184
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪</i>

568
00:41:29,253 --> 00:41:32,955
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

569
00:41:33,024 --> 00:41:36,058
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  AND YOU WILL BE FREE ♪</i>
YOU START SPEAKING IN TONGUES,

570
00:41:36,127 --> 00:41:39,328
AND I'LL SEND YOU
ON TO THE NEXT LIFE
RIGHT HERE AND NOW.

571
00:41:39,397 --> 00:41:42,298
[ Chuckles ]
SORRY. IT KINDA REMINDS ME
OF GOIN' WITH MY COUSIN NEWT...

572
00:41:42,366 --> 00:41:46,068
TO THE SLIPPERY ROCK CHURCH
OF THE GREAT REDEEMER
WHEN I WAS A KID.

573
00:41:46,137 --> 00:41:49,071
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

574
00:41:49,140 --> 00:41:52,074
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  AND YOU WILL BE FREE ♪</i>
HI. THANKS FOR COMIN'.

575
00:41:52,143 --> 00:41:55,744
<i>SORRY. STANDIN' ROOM ONLY.</i>
WE'RE NOT HERE
TO WORSHIP, REVEREND.

576
00:41:55,813 --> 00:41:58,079
PASTOR. I'M PASTOR JONES.

577
00:41:58,148 --> 00:42:01,316
<i> PASTOR JONES, WE</i>
<i> ARE LOOKING FOR THIS MAN.</i>
<i> THE NAME IS JAROD.</i>

578
00:42:01,385 --> 00:42:05,420
<i> WE BELIEVE HE'S INVOLVED</i>
<i> IN A CONFRONTATION WITH</i>
<i> A RACIST NAMED BARTLETT.</i>

579
00:42:05,489 --> 00:42:08,924
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  AND YOU WILL BE FREE ♪</i>

580
00:42:08,993 --> 00:42:11,260
I'M SORRY.
NEVER SEEN HIM BEFORE.

581
00:42:11,329 --> 00:42:14,763
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

582
00:42:14,832 --> 00:42:18,967
NOW, I DO KNOW ABOUT BARTLETT.
IF YOU WANNA TALK TO HIM,
TRY THE STATE PENITENTIARY.

583
00:42:19,036 --> 00:42:21,837
GOOD. I HOPE THEY
FRY HIS ASS THIS TIME.

584
00:42:21,906 --> 00:42:23,839
WELL, MA'AM,
IT'S MY HOPE AND PRAYER...

585
00:42:23,908 --> 00:42:26,508
THAT ONE DAY BARTLETT WILL
CHOOSE TO END THAT LIFE OF HATE.

586
00:42:26,577 --> 00:42:29,445
-<i> ♪♪ [ Singing Continues ]</i>
- AND START THE HEALIN'...

587
00:42:29,513 --> 00:42:32,948
THAT ONLY LOVE
AND FORGIVENESS WILL BRING.

588
00:42:33,017 --> 00:42:37,119
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

589
00:42:37,188 --> 00:42:40,088
- BETTER PRAY FOR ALL OF US.
- GOD BLESS YOU.

590
00:42:40,157 --> 00:42:43,959
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>   LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪</i>

591
00:42:44,028 --> 00:42:45,994
PASTOR JONES,
THANK YOU KINDLY.

592
00:42:46,064 --> 00:42:48,797
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS
OPEN UP YOUR HEART ♪

593
00:42:48,866 --> 00:42:52,734
♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS
LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS ♪

594
00:42:52,803 --> 00:42:56,505
<i>♪ LAY DOWN YOUR BURDENS</i>
<i>  AND YOU WILL BE FREE ♪</i>

